  "text": "Flies were raised on standard medium at 25uC on a 12/12 hr light/dark schedule. Flies used in this paper were w Fit1 KG05576 , and Fit2 EY08530 were obtained from the Bloomington stock centre. HandC-GAL4 4.2 [CITATION_1] (Hand-Gal4) flies were kindly provided by A. Paululat. HandC-GAL4; tub-GAL80 ts , UAS-Fit1 VDRC ; UAS-Fit2 VDRC , and HandC-GAL4; Fit1 D161 UAS-Fit2 VDRC flies were generated following standard crosses. Vienna Drosophila RNAi Centre (VDRC) RNAi lines used -Fit1 (#46494), Fit2 (#37010), and Mys (#29619). Transgenic RNAi Project (TRiP) RNAi lines used -Fit1 (#25966).",
